    "<em>Art and Illusion</em> laid the framework for a psychological understanding of art to a wider public.": [],
    "He became director of the Warburg in 1959.": [],
    "As director, he reorganized the institute, encouraging its scholars, who now included <a href=\"/wittkowerr\">Rudolf Wittkower</a>, <a href=\"/buchthalh\">Hugo Buchthal</a> and Kurz, to teach as well as research.": [],
